🍕 Project Concept “FoodieHub” (Food Delivery MERN App)

You’ll build a mini SwiggyZomato clone focused only on Pizza, Burgers, and Snacks.
Users can browse items, add to cart, place orders, and admins can manage menu items.

🧱 Core Features
👤 User Side (Frontend)

View all available food items (pizza, burgers, drinks, etc.)

Filter by category (Pizza 🍕  Burger 🍔  Drinks 🥤)

Add to cart, update quantity, remove items

Authentication (Login  Register)

Checkout (Order Summary)

View order history

🧑‍🍳 Admin Side

Login as Admin

Add new food items (with image, price, category)

Edit  Delete items

View all customer orders

Update order status (Pending → Preparing → Out for Delivery → Delivered)

💳 Optional (Advanced Add-ons)

Online payment integration (Stripe  Razorpay)

Order tracking (real-time with Socket.io)

Email confirmation after order

Ratings & reviews for dishes

🧠 Key Learning You’ll Get

✅ REST APIs with Express + MongoDB
✅ JWT authentication & role-based access (useradmin)
✅ Image uploads with Multer + Cloudinary
✅ State management (React Context or Redux)
✅ Integration between backend and frontend
✅ Clean folder structure & deployment

